Package: circglmbayes
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Analysis of a Circular GLM
Version: 1.2.1
Authors@R: person("Kees", "Mulder", 
           email = "keestimmulder@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Kees Mulder <keestimmulder@gmail.com>
Description: This package contains functions to perform a Bayesian circular GLM,
  which allows regressing a circular outcome on linear and categorical predictors. 
